import React from "react";
const Seo = (props) => (
   <>
         <title>{props.title}</title>
         <meta name="description" content={props.description}></meta>
         <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon" />
         <meta itemProp="name" content="Redefining Student Accommodation" />
         <meta itemProp="description" content="Compare, consult & choose your Student Accommodation from a wide range of premium and affordable student flats, lodges, studio apartments, ensuites, premium halls and more near your university.  ✔Property Consultation  ✔Student Loan  ✔Concierge Services  ✔Guarantor  ✔Community  ✔Visa Consultation." />
         <meta name="keywords" content="uniacco, uniacco.com, student accommodation, university accommodation, student housing, student flats, student lodge" />

         <meta property="og:title" content="Student Accommodation ◆ Compare, Consult & Choose ◆ UniAcco" />
         <meta property="og:description" content="Compare, consult & choose your Student Accommodation from a wide range of premium and affordable student flats, lodges, studio apartments, ensuites, premium halls and more near your university.  ✔Property Consultation  ✔Student Loan  ✔Concierge Services  ✔Guarantor  ✔Community  ✔Visa Consultation." />
         <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
         <meta property="og:url" content="https://uniacco.com/" />
         <meta property="og:image" content="https://uniacco.com/buildings@2x.jpg" />

         <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary"/>
         <meta name="twitter:title" content="Student Accommodation ◆ Compare, Consult & Choose ◆ UniAcco"/>
         <meta name="twitter:description" content="Compare, consult & choose your Student Accommodation from a wide range of premium and affordable student flats, lodges, studio apartments, ensuites, premium halls and more near your university.  ✔Property Consultation  ✔Student Loan  ✔Concierge Services  ✔Guarantor  ✔Community  ✔Visa Consultation."/>
         <meta name="twitter:image:src" content="https://uniacco.com/buildings@2x.jpg" />
   </>
);

export default Seo;
